title: Daryl Hall -Live from Daryl's House Part 6.WebRip.[PSoul].flv
description:
Live from Daryl&#039;s House (not from Daryl&#039;s House) Part 6 (WebRip)

Recorded live at SXSW in Austin, TX

Featuring:
Tom "T-Bone" Wolk (Guitars, Background vocals)
Eliot Lewis (Keyboards, Background Vocals)
Zev Katz (Bass)
Shawn Pelton (Drums)
Everett Bradley (Percussion, Background Vocals)

LFDH-6_1

1) You Make My Dreams
2) Everything Your Heart Desires
3) Cab Driver

LFDH-6_2

4) I Can&#039;t Stop Dreaming
5) Someone Like You
6) It&#039;s Uncanny

Comment: This was shown on Direct TV in the U.S. a couple of weeks ago. Needless to say the camera work is 100x better than previous episodes but as this was not from Daryl&#039;s house and has no special guest (nor a debut song) it seems a bit "off topic" for the series to date.
